    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a cross-flow cylinder head for exceptional volumetric efficiency. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, featuring reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension geometry for neutral handling. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain remains precise up to the 8,000 RPM redline. This is a mechanically sound, analog performance machine ready for the twisties.",
